{"tid":2144611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美制裁香港官員　黃國健料有關人士有心理準備影響不大","createTime":"2020-08-07T16:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T19:07:49.000Z","uid":90838,"like":88,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"085c3f1269f4dfa138cbb5683adf9c4790bac60e","tid":2144611,"uid":90838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:29:15.000Z","msg":"美國財政部公布制裁名單、包括多名香港官員。行政會議成員黃國健表示，相信有關人士已經有心理準備，認為對他們影響不大。他表示，除非相關人士於美國有很多資產或關係，但由於美方作出制裁的說法已經有一段時間，相信有關人士已經處理好問題。但他認為，前警務處處長盧偉聰較為無辜，因為通過港區國安法時，他已經離職。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，因為事件涉及外交，不知道特區政府可以作出哪些回應，認為應該要歸中央處理。被問到會否擔心行政會議成員會被列入制裁名單，他說如果被制裁會是他的光榮，但認為機會不大。<br />\n<br />\nSource:RTHK<br />\n<br />\n睇下撐到幾時先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e462c4378807e2abf341733463e6bcea8eb950c","tid":2144611,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:31:04.000Z","msg":"【多圖】政府要你飲嘅水同打嘅針 原來係咁得人驚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144594</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"56e1bce75d1f4b1038a2fd22ade9d6e8c30c7621","tid":2144611,"uid":224533,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:31:33.000Z","msg":"機會不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1b72a79586da78b6f68c8b69f0b9f30ed7a54e","tid":2144611,"uid":127575,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:32:12.000Z","msg":"有崑崙銀行<br />\n唔使驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff724d1db645dca15e348f6a13dbecd2656f5aa1","tid":2144611,"uid":66221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:33:02.000Z","msg":"咁唔通話求你原諒我咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4b1dc526ec90294df1af75f9e38b20ae520322","tid":2144611,"uid":5195,"like":14,"dislike":0,"sco